\fs29 \cf2 ME  \
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs21 \cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Anyone ever have car trouble?  Of course, you have\'85we all have.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The funny thing about car trouble is while everyone has it some do a better job navigating it than others.  \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf3 Illustration of me running out of Gas\'85I felt as though I was good.  I felt as though I had plenty of fuel.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf4 Transition: \'a0But when it comes to cars we all know how you feel doesn\'92t matter  (3:00)\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs29 \cf2 WE\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs21 \cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}When that light is on it doesn\'92t matter how you feel?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}When the fuel gauge is empty it doesn\'92t matter how you feel?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}When the temp is too hot it doesn\'92t matter if you feel it is just right!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You would feel LOST if you got in a car with no gauges \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}But what is so obvious in the world of cars, we miss in our own personal world.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We focus so much on how we feel\'85(explain)\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf5 Transition: Over the next few weeks I want to give you 4 gauge I think we all need to steal from a car and apply to our personal world.  (3:00)\
\
\
