\fs29 \cf2 GOD\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs21 \cf2 If you have a Bible I want to ask you to turn to Exodus ch. 18\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs20 \cf6 \super 13\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub The next day Moses took his seat to serve as judge for the people, and they stood around him from morning till evening.\'a0\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0
\fs23 \cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This is Moses new life. \'a0He was a leader for a while and now he is sitting in as judge.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It\'92s a long day - from morning till evening\'a0just listening to people\'92s problems.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}How many of you think that would get draining.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Every day Moses gets up and helps others all day.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs20 \cf6 \super 14\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub When his father-in-law saw all that Moses was doing for the people, he said, \'93What is this you are doing for the people? Why do you alone sit as judge, while all these people stand around you from morning till evening?\'94\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0\cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}His father-in-law sees it clearly!\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl1\cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}He\'92s\'a0exhausted\'a0and going to burn out\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}He\'92s doing too much and he\'92s\'a0asking the right questions.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0
\f0\b \cf7 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Sometimes it\'a0takes someone outside of the situation to say something to you that you can\'92t see yourself.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0
\f1\b0 \cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}But also what we see is Moses is doing too much.\'a0\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl1\cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}He\'92s busy!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It\'92s important to note this isn\'92t a bad thing\'85it\'92s a good thing he is doing.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It\'92s just too much\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0\cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And in the next verse we discover the issue that every single person struggles with at some point in time.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0
\f0\b \cf7 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Question: \'a0Do you ever feel as though you just get in the morning and are on the go until evening\'85all the while to do it the next day and the next day\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf7 \
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0
\f1\b0 \cf6 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Moses answered him, \'93Because the people come to me to seek God\'92s will.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf6 \
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0
\fs23 \cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}People need me.\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl1\cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}They need me\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}If I\'a0don\'92t\'a0do something they\'92ll be lost\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And it\'92s a good thing right? \'a0I\'92m helping others which is selfless so it must be good.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs20 \cf6 \super 16\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Whenever they have a dispute,\'a0it is brought to me, and I decide between the parties and inform them of God\'92s decrees and instructions.\'94\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf6 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl0\cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Not only do people need me\'85I\'92m the only one!\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\li360\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf6 Moses\'92 father-in-law replied, \'93What you are doing is not good.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf6 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0\cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It might feel good\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl1\cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It might seem good\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}But it is NOT good\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}There is a pace for everyone and the problem is we are too busy!\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0\cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Can you relate?\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\li360\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf6 You and these people who come to you will only wear yourselves out. The work is too heavy for you; you cannot handle it alone.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf6 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl0\cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}He says something here so important about time management, stress, and work load.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}That when you are overworked\'85it will overwork others!\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl1\cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Blow up on kids\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Bail out on responsibilities\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Rack up debt because you couldn\'92t do what you needed to do\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Ruin a healthy marriage\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\li360\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf6 Listen now to me and I will give you some 
\f2\i\b advice
\f1\i0\b0 , and may God be with you.\'a0You must be the people\'92s representative before God and bring their disputes\'a0to him.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf6 \
\pard\pardeftab720\li360\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf6 \
\
\'a0
\f0\b\fs20 \super 20\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Teach them his decrees and instructions, and show them the way they are to live\'a0and how they are to behave.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf6 \
\
\'a0
\f0\b\fs20 \super 21\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub But select capable men\'a0from all the people\'97men who fear\'a0God, trustworthy men who hate dishonest gain\'97and appoint them as officials\'a0over thousands, hundreds, fifties and tens.\
\
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs20 \cf6 \super 24\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Moses listened to his father-in-law and did everything he said.\'a0\cf2  \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs21 \cf8 Transition: In this passage Moses does three things I want us to be able to do in order to make the shift we need to make (10 min)\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs29 \cf2 YOU\
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs24 \cf2 Calling vs Callers\
\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls10\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs21 \cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The problem is your callers will always outnumber you calling and if you\'92re not careful you\'92ll be stuck.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Moses couldn\'92t distinguish the two.  \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You\'92ve got to say NO\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}You\'92ve got to let some callers go to voicemail\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Evaluate the call\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The phone is for you, not for them!\
\pard\pardeftab720\li720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf3 Illustration of being in a deep conversation with someone and the phone beeps.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf5 Transition:  His calling was to teach the people the ways of God so they could follow Him, his callers wanted him to do just that\'85which made it confusing and complicated\'85which leads me to my next point: (5 Min)\
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs24 \cf2 Method vs Motive\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs21 \cf2 Moses was trying to live out his motive \'96 helping people live in tune with God\'92s calling but was using a bad method.  You know you can do the right thing the wrong way.  You can have the best motives in the world and still kill yourself doing it the wrong way.\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf7 The problem is we combine the two and every time someone challenges our Methods we feel like they are challenging our Motive\
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0 \cf2 People who struggle with this:\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls11\ilvl0\cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Parents who take short cuts in parenting or do too much\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf7 There are some people counting on you today to make a shift in your life \'96 to challenge NOT your motives but your Methods\
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf9 Transition:  And how do you do that?  So glad you asked because it is the last thing Moses did\'85 (5 min)\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs24 \cf2 Revelation vs Reason\
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs21 \cf2 Do you know why I read a lot of self help books\'85because they are helpful!\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf3 Illustration of people who tell me that if God wanted them to know something He would tell them Himself\'85that\'92s stupid and bad theology\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf2 I believe the revelation that God wants to give us will come from Him directly but never discount someone else\'92s reason!\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf7 Moses didn\'92t realize he was in bad shape?  It was just normal life?  Are you open to a beautiful accident!\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf10 \'93Ancient Israel did not fall into the theological trap of polarizing the accidental and the eternal.\'94 \'a0Commentary\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf10 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs21 \cf2 It would have been so easy for Moses to say \'93You\'92re not even suppose to be here Jethro\'94.  I mean that name even has a Beverly Hillbilly\'92s tone to it doesn\'92t it?\
\
\
Ways you get reason and challenge your methods:\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls12\ilvl0\cf2 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Small Groups\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Books\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Sermons \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Podcasts\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Blogs\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Mentors  -  drop the fall about GOSPEL\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf4 Transition:  And if you do these three things something else will SHIFT (5 Min) (32 min)\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs29 \cf2 WE\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\fs21 \cf3 Illustration of a Tachometer vs a Speedometer\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls13\ilvl0
